    m_Localized: Sleepy Hollow
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17286964699000832
    m_Localized: 'Assault the sleepy hollow village in your annual resurrection on
      October 31st.


      Throw the dice and try to get as many souls as you can.
      You need 20 to challenge the boss in the Church.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17302750679330816
    m_Localized: Quit Game
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17302838784880640
    m_Localized: Are you sure you want to quit the game? Any unsaved data will be
      lost.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
