  - m_Id: 17313360771084288
    m_Localized: Poison
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63657728255520768
    m_Localized: Deals damage each turn, decreasing both Health Points (HP) and Mana
      Points (MP).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63657756210556928
    m_Localized: Deals true damage each turn until it's active.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 64057128463167488
    m_Localized: '{stat}: {value}'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1771278204849094873
  - m_Id: 64726282702745600
    m_Localized: '<b>Attack</b> - Dullahan swings their sword and deals PHY DMG.
      This attack cannot kill an enemy, leaving the enemy at 1 HP. When the enemy
      is left with 1 HP, this attacks turns into <b>Kill</b>.


      <b>Kill</b>
      - Dullahan severs the head to the enemy and kills it, ending the battle.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65140046900031488
    m_Localized: Staggered
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65140214496030720
    m_Localized: Dullahan tries to act, but can't move.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65140133143310336
    m_Localized: The unit affected is staggered and cannot act for the next turn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
